    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos overhaul. The chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from refreshed bushings and a factory-spec limited-slip differential that ensures predictable rotation. While the finish reflects its status as a dedicated driver's car, the powertrain remains exceptionally tight, pulling hard to the 8,000 RPM redline with no hesitation. It\u2019s an honest, performance-oriented build ready for the canyons or the track.",
